## 6. PERFORMANCE CONSIDERATIONS

### Page Load Optimization
- Implement **lazy loading** for product images
- Use **pagination** (12-24 items per page)
- Cache category listings (3600 seconds)
- Cache bestseller products (1800 seconds)
- Minify CSS/JavaScript

### Database Queries
- Always use `select()` to load only needed columns
- Use `pluck()` for single column results
- Implement query logging in development
- Monitor slow queries (> 100ms)

```php
// Bad
$products = Product::all();

// Good
$products = Product::select('id', 'name', 'slug', 'price', 'image_url')
    ->where('is_active', true)
    ->paginate(12);
```

---

## 7. SECURITY BEST PRACTICES

- **Validate all input**: Use Form Requests
- **Sanitize output**: Use Blade's `{{ }}` (auto-escaping)
- **CSRF protection**: Include `@csrf` in all forms
- **Rate limiting**: Implement on API routes
- **File uploads**: Validate type, size, scan for malware
- **SQL Injection prevention**: Always use parameterized queries (Laravel does this by default)

---

## 8. CODE EXAMPLES

### Product Repository
```php
<?php
namespace App\Repositories;

use App\Models\Product;
use Illuminate\Pagination\Paginator;

class ProductRepository
{
    public function getFeaturedProducts(int $limit = 12): array
    {
        return Product::with(['category', 'images'])
            ->where('is_active', true)
            ->where('is_featured', true)
            ->limit($limit)
            ->get()
            ->toArray();
    }
    
    public function getProductsByCategory(string $categorySlug, int $page = 1): Paginator
    {
        return Product::with(['category', 'images'])
            ->whereHas('category', fn($q) => $q->where('slug', $categorySlug))
            ->where('is_active', true)
            ->paginate(12);
    }
    
    public function searchProducts(string $query, int $page = 1): Paginator
    {
        return Product::with(['category', 'images'])
            ->where('is_active', true)
            ->where(function($q) use ($query) {
                $q->where('name', 'like', "%{$query}%")
                  ->orWhere('description', 'like', "%{$query}%")
                  ->orWhere('meta_keywords', 'like', "%{$query}%");
            })
            ->paginate(12);
    }
}
```

### Product Service
```php
<?php
namespace App\Services;

use App\Repositories\ProductRepository;

class ProductService
{
    private ProductRepository $repository;
    
    public function __construct(ProductRepository $repository)
    {
        $this->repository = $repository;
    }
    
    public function getProductsForDisplay(string $category = null): array
    {
        if ($category) {
            return $this->repository->getProductsByCategory($category)->toArray();
        }
        
        return $this->repository->getFeaturedProducts();
    }
}
```

